(firstQuint)Tilt-Table Study of the Clinical Efficacy of Midodrine in Symptomatic Orthostatic Hypotension.

 The efficacy of midodrine will be assessed in those subjects who have severe symptoms of orthostatic hypotension when not taking midodrine and are controlled when taking midodrine.

 The study will involve approximately 4 overnight stays.

.

 Tilt-Table Study of the Clinical Efficacy of Midodrine in Symptomatic Orthostatic Hypotension@highlight

The purpose of this study is to determine whether midodrine works against the symptoms of orthostatic hypotension caused by being on a tilt table.

